346
00:25:12,292 --> 00:25:14,532
Is Mr. Qiang Qingci not coming today?

347
00:25:14,532 --> 00:25:15,971
He has something urgent to deal with.

348
00:25:15,971 --> 00:25:18,372
He's busier than any of us.

349
00:25:18,372 --> 00:25:21,812
