351
00:25:23,651 --> 00:25:24,491
She means you.

352
00:25:24,491 --> 00:25:25,612
We didn't scare anyone.

353
00:25:25,612 --> 00:25:26,731
- Who...
- Scaring people

354
00:25:26,731 --> 00:25:27,451
