00:28:18,061 --> 00:28:19,372
Shengshengman is definitely not simple.

404
00:28:19,372 --> 00:28:20,612
- Right.
- She and Mr. Mo...

405
00:28:23,132 --> 00:28:24,092
Mr. Mo.

