434
00:30:59,216 --> 00:31:02,128
♪Slowly, slowly, we fall in love♪

435
00:31:02,128 --> 00:31:04,624
♪Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you♪

436
00:31:05,251 --> 00:31:09,852
