440
00:31:15,931 --> 00:31:18,731
Are you listening to all theirs
or just hers?

441
00:31:20,731 --> 00:31:21,372
Everyone's.

442
00:31:24,251 --> 00:31:26,332
Sheng, come out and rest a bit.

443
00:31:28,411 --> 00:31:28,971
Okay.

444
00:31:31,891 --> 00:31:32,772
