486
00:34:16,291 --> 00:34:17,291
Doudou.

487
00:34:17,291 --> 00:34:20,211
My favorite place is here, the pantry.

488
00:34:21,932 --> 00:34:23,412
Doudou.

489
00:34:23,412 --> 00:34:26,492
